summary: I am selling a white 2009 Mazda CX-9 with 139 000km. It is a fully-loaded Grand Touring Edition with sunroof, heated leather seats, blind spot monitors, Bose sound, bluetooth, cruise contol, a navigation system, and two TV's with DVD players in the rear headrests. The interior and exterior are in very good shape. The car was recently waxed and the paint is in excellent condition. There have been no accidents and I am the second owner (the previous owner was my father, so the vehicle has stayed in the family).

I am selling a 2010 Ford F-150 that is in very good shape. The truck has some great features: leather seats, sunroof, bluetooth, trailer tow package, power seats, power locks, and heated seats. It has been well maintained and has always been kept up to date with synthetic oil changes. It's a clean truck, inside and out.

Experience the HellCat 'Viagara'. Guaranteed to get you 'up' and running. The brand new Charger HellCat demo looks awesome, sounds awesome! There is plenty of power to spare: 707hp from a 6.2L supercharged hemi! The Charger is fully loaded with navigation, sunroof, heated / ventilated seats, and much more.
The Mercedes B200 features a 2.0L turbo engine. It is very clean and has just received new brakes and an oil change.
The MINI Cooper features a 1.6L engine that uses a timing chain. It is very clean and has just received new brakes and an oil change. All four tires are in good condition
The Mazda 3 Skyactive is a clean car with low mileage. It has heated leather seats and many more features.

The 2016 Chevrolet Malibu LT features air conditioning, alloy wheels, AM / FM radio, cruise control, floor mats, folding rear seats, power options, stability control, and telescopic and tilt steering. The vehicle is accident free, smoker free, and pet free.
I am selling a grey 2011 Chevrolet Malibu LS for $10 000. It is flex fuel capable and features bluetooth and power options.
This vehicle is a five-passenger sedan with alloy wheels. It features a USB port, a touch screen, and an auxiliary input. I am the original owner and it is accident free.
I am selling a white Chrysler Town & Country. It is both smoker free and pet free. It has satellite radio, a CD player, an MP3 decoder, and DVD audio.
Features CD player, premium sound, XM satellite, Bluetooth Wireless, keyless start, alloy wheels, and privacy glass

Has a clean black interior, cloth seats, all-power options, a tow package, tinted windows, an MBRP exhaust, and aftermarket head-lights and tail-lights. All fluids are regularly maintained and there are no scratches on the wheels
I am selling a red 2013 Nissan Versa that runs well. It is a great economy car that gets around 37MPG at highway speed.
Features power steering, tilt wheel, AM / FM stereo, CD, air conditioning, power windows, power door locks, cruise control, dual airbags, and steel wheels
The Nissan Altima has MP3. Bluetooth Wireless, keyless entry, keyless start, backup camera, dual airbags, side airbags, F&R head curtain airbags, and steel wheels.

This is as nice of a used Jeep as you can get. It has a lot of extras. I bought it with great intentions and never used it. It has never been off-road and has no damage. I had the following parts added by my dealer: 4in lift and steering correction, high steer drag link, bracket relocation, adjustable rear control arms with spring correction brackets, a one tonne rear drive shaft, 35" BF Goodrich all-terrain tires with a spare, a warn bumper and winch, and an LED light bar and pods with a pillar guard

We will consider a decent trade or an RV motorhome. It is very clean and has been smoker-, pet-, and child-free. It is well maintained and has been on a maintenance schedule with the company that the owner currently works for.

I am selling my Impreza. I rarely drive it. It runs great and the interior was swapped out with blue and black leather seats. All the brakes have been redone, except for the front rotors. I just did an oil change and tested the air conditioning.
Our Tundra features power windows, power locks, power seats, keyless entry, remote start, a spray-in liner, a tonneau cover, a back-up camera, TRD exhaust, fog lamps, and bluetooth phone.
